2259
03:07:38,897 --> 03:07:45,539
on the school side for a number of years, doing municipal aggregation on the school side.

2260
03:07:46,159 --> 03:07:57,203
And back in 2014, it was reported in the Meffitt transcript that, and the article reads, Meffitt Unplugs on electricity contract cost schools more than $100,000, Mr. President.

2261
03:08:00,151 --> 03:08:17,014
The city, when they went in and purchased on behalf of the schools, failed to renew the contract and had to go back out on the open market and wasn't able to obtain a rate like they had when they had a contract.

2262
03:08:17,374 --> 03:08:23,655
And it ended up costing the schools, which is you and I the rate payer, $100,000 because they failed to do their job.

2263
03:08:26,616 --> 03:08:33,524
So after that glowing recommendation, now they say, you know what, let's do it on behalf of every resident in this community.

2264
03:08:33,984 --> 03:08:35,086
Look at our track record.

2265
03:08:35,386 --> 03:08:39,450
Now we want to bring in every resident and we'll go out on your behalf.

2266
03:08:39,851 --> 03:08:43,595
Anytime the government wants to get involved in your business, Mr. President,

2267
03:08:43,875 --> 03:08:46,137
as far as I'm concerned, is not a win-win.

2268
03:08:46,657 --> 03:08:52,142
When the government says, we want to save you money, that should be the biggest red flag.

2269
03:08:52,162 --> 03:08:56,005
Because the government is not in business to save you or I money.

2270
03:08:56,605 --> 03:08:58,527
They're not in that business, Mr. President.

2271
03:08:58,947 --> 03:09:04,311
So this will get its proper hearing in the Energy Subcommittee, Mr. President.

2272
03:09:04,812 --> 03:09:07,013
But as far as I'm concerned, I agree with the Speaker.

2273
03:09:08,014 --> 03:09:09,796
When the state legislature created this,

2274
03:09:10,458 --> 03:09:15,221
They created a clause where it says it's voluntary in the law.

2275
03:09:15,662 --> 03:09:16,783
This is voluntary.

2276
03:09:17,123 --> 03:09:22,186
However, once your city council votes for it, it's no longer voluntary.

2277
03:09:22,687 --> 03:09:26,049
