2279
03:09:29,672 --> 03:09:38,378
And we all know when we changed our meters over, it took us several years just to change our meters over in this city because people weren't properly informed.

2280
03:09:39,469 --> 03:09:45,732
And to say that there'll be community outreach and so forth, they made a big mistake with the legislation.

2281
03:09:46,052 --> 03:09:47,453
